Package: skinCellTypeAnnotation
Title: Reference-Based Cell Type Annotation for Human Skin scRNA-seq
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Lukas", "Henning", email = "lukas@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: Automated cell type annotation pipeline for human skin scRNA-seq data
    using the Reynolds et al. 2021 human skin cell atlas reference. Performs 
    reference-based label transfer to annotate query datasets with 34+ cell types.
Depends: R (>= 4.2.0)
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports: 
    Seurat (>= 5.0.0),
    anndata (>= 0.10.0),
    dplyr,
    ggplot2
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
